column3: Relations defined by DCMI Metadata Terms: http://dublincore.org/documents/dcmi-terms/
Relations defined by the Bibliographic Ontology (BIBO): http://bibotools.googlecode.com/svn/bibo-ontology/trunk/doc/index.html
Relations defined by the Friend of a Friend vocabulary (FOAF): http://xmlns.com/foaf/spec/
Relations defined by the Functional Requirements for Bibliographic Records (FRBR): http://vocab.org/frbr/core.html
Custom vocabulary containing relations defined for this Omeka instance.
The BIO vocabulary contains terms useful for finding out more about people and their backgrounds and has some cross-over into genealogical information.
